          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Both of my kids have been studying at MRIS 51 since the last 3-4 years. My son passed out 10th last year and has transferred to MRIS 46 now. My daughter is in 1st grade right now. I would say that it is a brilliant school and I am extremely satisfied. The teachers are extremely good mentors for our children. All of them are very polite and approachable. Even the extra curricular activities are very diverse and help our children to develop all round skills in all activities.\n\nI am thankful to all the teachers, headmistress ma'am, and last but definitely not the least, Principal ma'am. All of them are always ready to help.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
