          "reviewBody": "A good school by all means. Our daughter has been studying here since Nursery class and her overall personality development has been good. The teachers are interactive and approachable. There's a nice meals service available. Though there are a few Sports facilities inhouse but what's lacking is a big playground.",
          "publisher": {
