            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am parent of two kids both studying at manav rachna international school sector 51, gurgaon. So I am kind of involved with school since 11 years now. I must say the school is really caring for children's overall development.\n\nTeachers who are pillars of this school are so deserving and such graceful mentors for our kids. They are so hardworking and creative as well to understand the need of every individual child to polish them at their best.\n\nSpecially the education system for the growing years the school possess is commendable.\n\nThankful to every teacher, staff members , headmistress and principal ma'am who are just a call away in case of any urgency regarding child. They are always there to support and provide immediate help.",
